* BMAP phase-7 macros: MACRO/ENDM definition, #N positional substitution, and
* a macro that calls another macro (nested expansion).  ADD2 a,b -> ADA a/ADA b;
* DBL n -> ADD2 n,n.  ADA n = 0oNNNNNN075000.
       OUNAME MACTST
ADD2   MACRO
       ADA    #1
       ADA    #2
       ENDM
DBL    MACRO
       ADD2   #1,#1
       ENDM
       LDA    0
       ADD2   3,5
       DBL    7
       END
